Interface IContactConfigPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface IContactConfigPlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    Plugin that customizes Contact behavior, particularly in how it interacts with PolicyContactRole and AccountContactRole.
